  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is Xeno, a space story inspired by the atmosphere of old flash games in which you will experience many adventures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.poster.avif?t=1739796413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.webm?t=1739796413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.mp4?t=1739796413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/7887c92f9cd0f0043ba7a99dc6762394.avif?t=1739796413\" width=660 height=621 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xeno is a 2D platform game - we move left and right and jump in the game, we can shoot and, in some cases, sneak to eliminate enemies from hiding. The game will also feature the use of the environment, such as exoskeletons or vehicles of all types, and puzzles. The gameplay focuses mainly on fighting bosses, which become more and more diverse and more difficult with new stages. There are also arcade elements to diversify the gameplay</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is Xeno, a space story inspired by the atmosphere of old flash games in which you will experience many adventures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.poster.avif?t=1739796413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.webm?t=1739796413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/9477901b030c0a54f0870bb1ae9ceee0.mp4?t=1739796413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903940/extras/7887c92f9cd0f0043ba7a99dc6762394.avif?t=1739796413\" width=660 height=621 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xeno is a 2D platform game - we move left and right and jump in the game, we can shoot and, in some cases, sneak to eliminate enemies from hiding. The game will also feature the use of the environment, such as exoskeletons or vehicles of all types, and puzzles. The gameplay focuses mainly on fighting bosses, which become more and more diverse and more difficult with new stages. There are also arcade elements to diversify the gameplay</p>",
